Title: Knicknack's Knickknacks
Description:
Not fair! Not fair! Knicknack collect many shiny things over long life. But now stupid wax for brains Candleclaws push out Knicknack and family. Shiny things all left behind!

Here, goblin friend helped made list of all my treasures inside Darkflame Cleft. You go take back!
ObjectivesText: Retrieve Knicknack's treasures from Darkflame Cleft.
CompletionText: Treasures all very important. Very valuable. You no take for you! Bring back to me!
RewardText: You did it! You did it! My treasures! Take that, stupid Candleclaws.
